HEADWORD: Incuriosity
<hw>In*cu`ri*os"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>incuriositas</ets>: cf. F. <ets>incurosit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Lack of curiosity or interest; inattentiveness; indifference.</def>
